==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sparkling
<hw>Spar"kling</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Emitting sparks;
glittering; flashing; brilliant; lively; <as>as, <ex>sparkling</ex>
wine; <ex>sparkling</ex> eyes.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Spar"kling*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Spar"kling*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Brilliant; shining. See
<er>Shining</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spark plug</ent>⟦br⟧
